      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a high-quality finish with only minor, expected signs of use, such as small stone chips on the hood. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all electronic features and climate control systems functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, offering a smooth ride and reliable performance for its next owner. It represents a great balance of value and quality for someone looking for a dependable, attractive vehicle.",
