    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty in person. It is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have taken such meticulous care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for that 'brand-new' feel without the dealership price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'm happy to answer any questions, so just reach out! \u2728",
