    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the celebrated S54 3.2L inline-six engine, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically optimized, the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with VAC coated bearings, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure torsional rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise gate engagement, paired with a factory variable M differential lock for exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis retains all original bushings and suspension geometry, offering the tactile feedback only a low-mileage, well-preserved E46 can provide. Finished in Carbon Black with a flawless underside, this is a turnkey specimen for the performance purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2022 Model X. Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Full service records available. Clean title.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
