    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since its original purchase. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster with no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather seating remains firm and supple with absolutely no bolster wear or creasing, and it still retains that distinct new-car scent. Every technological feature, from the panoramic infotainment system to the ambient lighting, operates with precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its history of fair-weather use only. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a 'time capsule' vehicle in pristine condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
