    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it drives like a total dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust on it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 42900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
